---
title: Warm Barley Salad with Butter Beans, Avocado, and Burst Tomatoes
description: We love a good grain salad – it’s all about the mix-ins! Here, we’re tossing together creamy butter beans, silky avocado, and burst tomatoes for a mixture of colours and textures. Torn basil adds a touch of lemony freshness to the dish.
